Title: Oaxaca-Blinder as a Reweighting Estimator 
Abstract:
 The classic regression based estimator of counterfactual means studied by
 Ronald Oaxaca (1973) and Alan Blinder (1973) is shown to constitute a
 propensity score reweighting estimator based upon a linear model for the
 conditional odds of being treated.
