Title: The Risky Steady State 
Abstract:
 We propose a simple quantitative method to linearize around the risky
 steady state of a small open economy. Unlike when the deterministic steady
 state is used, the net foreign asset position is well defined. We allow
 for stochastic income and stochastic interest rate.
